subfields.content: Eastern Association of Mosquito Control Workers (U.S.)
Description based on: Vol. 1, no. 3 (Aug. 1941); title from cover.
Vol. 3 the June issue includes a Directory of agencies engaged in mosquito work (corrections in following issue, v. 3.
Vols. for <Aug. 1941>-Mar. 1944 issued by: Eastern Association of Mosquito Control Workers; June 1944-Dec. 1948 by: American Mosquito Control Association.
Vols. for   include Proceedings of the annual meeting of the Utah Mosquito Abatement Association.
